# WebHook Manager

Python service scaffold using FastAPI, PostgreSQL (async), Redis, Celery, and Docker.

## Local development

Create a virtualenv and install:

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

Common commands:

```bash
make lint
make type-check
make test
make up
```

